Developer Terms of Use
des:
Brushing your teeth is an important part of your day and it is recommended that you brush for at least two minutes twice a day. This skill will time you for two minutes and beep at 30 second intervals to remind you to move to a new part of your mouth.

Just say "Alexa Brush your teeth" and off she'll go.
